{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cThe Book of Hiro\u201d is a 3D visual puzzle game developed by two independent developers. Players help Hero embark on an adventure to the palace, using illusions and perspective to solve puzzles and explore the magical world in this book.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Innovative Visual Puzzles]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features innovative visual puzzles that are imaginative and visually stunning. The innovative visual illusion finding gameplay involves moving the viewing angle, clicking, and other operations to find the hidden \u201ckey\u201d pattern in the picture. Each puzzle solved can advance the plot and provide a unique gaming experience and visual impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533870/extras/\u5207\u6362\u89d2\u5ea6.gif?t=1727409047\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Vivid 3D Graphics]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a simple and fresh 3D low-poly style that is full of childlike innocence while meticulously depicting the different scenes in the story. The game\u2019s soothing and distant music complements the graphics to create a mysterious visual pop-up book.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533870/extras/\u7acb\u4f53\u6545\u4e8b\u4e66.gif?t=1727409047\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Challenging Gameplay]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features shiny gold coins, ordinary keys, hammers, gears, and other objects that are common but difficult to find due to the game\u2019s unusual mechanics. Players must make bold guesses and not be fooled by seemingly unrelated images. They must carefully observe and remember that what they see is not necessarily what they get!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533870/extras/\u91d1\u5e01.gif?t=1727409047\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[Intriguing Storyline] </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features an energetic and art-inspired storybook style. Behind the seemingly ordinary protagonist\u2019s travel story is a hidden plot and an extraordinary experience. The game includes a main storyline and hidden endings waiting for you to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2533870/extras/\u6865+\u94a5\u5319.gif?t=1727409047\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Prologue - Welcome, Reader","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/45db4892a384eed564276f177759d1c5614db679.jpg"},{"name":"Introduction - Storyteller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/5a31c1e5b20758608da513497be57caea2449746.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter One - Early Morning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/bc420c2f97747f4441e44a383880352e3a28d976.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Two - Embarking on the Journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/3bc6d849c8b1f192f1388c7bc66588daf0820ff2.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Three - Brave Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/95e118fb1ceb34fbdb74703f8fa96089a37e523f.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Four - Demon King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/b8d4432c75b26412524f1b39d185d8651ce02be4.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Five - Escape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/b0acebaf0ab8b9df4a0f2378941b4e43c0c2d89d.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Six - Obstructed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2533870/786196340b4c74c3eaa51245cd93c7e5eb0cd7d0.jpg"},{"name":"Chapter Se